# Pre-push build

Before `git push` (or when the user asks to push), run the same checks CI runs locally and fix failures before pushing:

```bash
./scripts/ci-local.sh
```

For UI-only changes, at minimum:

```bash
./scripts/vercel-build-check.sh   # when root vercel.json / Git deploy path applies
cd frontend && npm run lint && npm run test:run && npm run build
```

Do not push if these fail. Report what failed and fix it first.
